TITLE: Episode 83 - Living Cage Free with Nicole Sauce [Adult Language]
DESCRIPTION: This week, we talk to Living Free in Tennessee's own Nicole Sauce. A woman compelled to reduce government involvement in everything, raise chickens, and cook really great food for her neighbors, she is clearly one of us. We discuss optimism, the numerous opportunities we have, and how to find your people.
